 and number 91 over the following two weeks before dropping out of the top 100.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20151127/7501/|title=Official Singles Chart Top 100 {{!}} Official Charts Company|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20151204/7501/|title=Official Singles Chart Top 100 {{!}} Official Charts Company|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref> In January 2016, the song re-entered the UK Singles Chart at number 69 following the release of the ''Keep Up'' EP.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/singles-chart/20160101/7501/|title=Official Singles Chart Top 100 {{!}} Official Charts Company|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref> The song also charted at number 78 on the [[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]] Australia Top 100 Singles Chart.<ref name=\":1\" />\n\n==Music video==\nThe music video, directed by Jack Delaney, was uploaded to KSI's YouTube channel on 15 November 2015, two days after the release of the song. As of April 2020, the music video has 40 million views.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uBosAirL8ds|title=KSI Ft. JME - KEEP UP (Official Video)|last=|first=|date=15 November 2015|website=YouTube|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref name=autogenerated2 />\n| title6 = \n| length10 = \n| title10 = \n| length9 = \n| title9 = \n| length8 = \n| title8 = \n| length7 = \n| title7 = \n| length6 = \n| length5 = \n| title1 = Keep Up\n| title5 = \n| length4 = \n| title4 = \n| length3 = \n| title3 = \n| length2 = \n| title2 = \n| all_writing = \n| length1 = 3:01\n| note1 = featuring [[Jme (musician)|Jme]]\n| total_length = \n}}\n\n== Credits and personnel ==\nCredits adapted from [[Tidal (service)|